close_reason: "Fixed GH-340 by setting detached telemetry flush worker cwd to os.tmpdir(), preventing Windows from locking caller temp project directories after foreground CLI exit. Verified targeted test, build, static quality, full 100/100/100/100 coverage, security scan, changelog check, health/validate, manual isolated temp smoke, and PR #341 CI/CodeQL/Windows regression."
